ton ate them whole!all the golems then converged on the glutton, and after a lot of fighting the beast was slain... and then, out of the corpse of the glutton... one defiant beetle rider burst out of the glutton's mouth, charging at the fethered serpants, he died soon after, but not before taking one of them down!this was when the other two matriarcs attacked! slaying the engineers outright! there were only one unit of golems and one unit of musketmen left!it was a desprate assault, it seemed hopeless since the musketmen were too overwhelmed to reload their muskets! and were dieing fast! there was one naga left and one golem left and one musketman left! single people! the golem grabbed the naga from behind, holding on to dear life! giving the musketman enough time to reload and fire at the matriarc! killing her!it was a phyric victory... the lost city was cleared... yet the only survivers... one golem pilot... and one musketeer...they were no longer an army, so they shook hands, and went their own ways...the lone musketeer left to the new city that needed the resources from the now cleared lost city, and is now teaching the local guardwhile the golem headed to the capital, it just so happened that the empress had a spot for a golem in her royal guard... he arived just in time...There ends my story,Certainly not mundane.Now i think it's time to,Play the damn game."
