,Recommended,226840,17227458,"Posted: 25 July, 2015",all,l3illdoom,"Simply an amazing strategy and tactical game. It's a fantasy-based Civ with less fluffy alternate win conditions and city building, and a much more detailed and satisfying combat element that takes place on a tactical battlefield with a plethora of spells and unit abilities to take advantage of.The new class system is meaningful and makes a significant difference in how you play, shaping your strategy while not committing you to a single path.If you're a fan of the series, it certainly lives up to the original games. If you haven't played the originals but enjoy strategy and/or tactical games, buy this now. It's worth full retail and is an absolute steal when on sale.Near infinite replayability due to the random map generator, combinations of class and race, different game ""paces"", etc. You'll have a blast."
